        '  ],\n'
        '  "mdd_amount_key": "qty_per_unit_mg",\n'
        '  "daily_units": 1,\n'
        '  "daily_unit_label": "unit/day",\n'
        '  "sections": [\n'
        '    {"name": "Composition", "rows": [\n'
        '      {"material_code": "", "ingredient": "", "function": "",\n'
        '       "status": "", "qty_per_unit_mg": ""}\n'
        '    ]}\n'
        '  ],\n'
        '  "packaging": [\n'
        '    {"material_code": "", "name": ""}\n'
        '  ]\n'
        '}\n\n'
        "Rules:\n"
        "- amount_columns keys must exactly match keys used in every row.\n"
        "- daily_units is the number of units/doses used for maximum daily intake. "
        "Use 1 for a single daily injection unless the sheet states otherwise.\n"
        "- If several strengths are present, choose mdd_amount_key for the worst-case "
